@host = http://localhost:5078

### MVC Home
GET {{host}}/

### Pages API
GET {{host}}/api/pages

### Places API
GET {{host}}/api/places

### Create a place
POST {{host}}/api/places
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "조용한 골목길",
  "category": "휴식",
  "description": "사람이 많지 않아 생각을 정리하기 좋은 길입니다.",
  "recommendedActivities": "산책, 글쓰기",
  "isVisited": false,
  "visitCount": 0,
  "latitude": 34.9512,
  "longitude": 127.4931,
  "isShared": true,
  "sharedDescription": "조용히 걷기 좋은 개인 추천 스팟입니다."
}

### Challenges API
GET {{host}}/api/challenges

### Register Identity API
POST {{host}}/api/identity/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@tracemap.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd"
}

### Login Identity API
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/identity/login?useCookies=false
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "administrator@tracemap.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd"
}

### Secure API with bearer token
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.accessToken}}
GET {{host}}/api/secure
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Me API
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
